bilingual.target: 拼写测试就像做梦一样。

bilingual.source: The spelling test was a piece of cake.
I have a listening test next week.
bilingual.target: 我下周有一个听力测试。
这是一个惊人的力量测试。

bilingual.source: After the test you can do the Fun and Games lesson.
bilingual.target: 测试后你可以进行趣味游戏课。

bilingual.source: He's come up with a new way to test his ideas.
bilingual.target: 他想出了一个测试他想法的新方法。

bilingual.source: Her new Ebola test is safe to transport and easy to use.
bilingual.target: 她的新埃博拉测试安全易用，便于运输。

bilingual.source: Liquid silk fibers could be used to make an Ebola test that did not need to be refrigerated.
bilingual.target: 液态蚕丝纤维可以用来制作不需要冷藏的埃博拉测试。

bilingual.source: As a test, six people lived in a Mars-like environment in Hawaii for a year before "returning to Earth" recently.
bilingual.target: 作为测试，六个人在夏威夷的类似火星的环境中生活了一年，最近“返回地球”。

bilingual.source: The tester worked late to finish the test cases.
bilingual.target: 测试员加班完成了测试用例。

list.abstract: test，意为测试，在中学课本中有出现，一般都以“学科名称+test”的形式出现，如：English test,Chinese test等。 还有一种解释是在软件中出现，一般用于检测软件好坏程度的单词当中。 此单词通俗易懂，意思简单。
Test命令将两个操作数进行逻辑与运算，并根据运算结果设置相关的标志位。但是，Test命令的两个操作数不会被改变。运算结果在设置过相关标记位后会被丢弃。

yingyinNormal.en: What were your test results?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的测试结果是什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Just take the test, B. Stop it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总之自己测试一下，B。别拿出来。

yingyinNormal.en: Looks like the professor is about to test a door!
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来教授要测试门了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd like to climb your hair, test that out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也想爬上你的头发测试一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Not because of a test or a Web site, but because...
yingyinNormal.zh: 不能因为一场测试或某个网站，而是因为...

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, I've been very stressed. I had that chem test on Friday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我最近烦躁，我星期五就作了测试。

yingyinNormal.en: Bravery test. First one to take his hand out is the sidekick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 勇敢度测试，先把手拿出来的人就是跟班。

yingyinNormal.en: That was a test, and you just failed. Damn it! Rookie mistake!
yingyinNormal.zh: 那是个测试，你没过关。该死的！新手失误！

yingyinNormal.en: That's not supposed to be a choice. The test should tell us what to do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 根本没有所谓的选择，测试应该告诉我们做什么。

yingyinNormal.en: And yet weren't there two accidents on your test track during a rainstorm?
yingyinNormal.zh: 但在暴风雨中的测试中是不是出现过两次事故？

yingyinNormal.en: Are you crazy? Perhaps. Are you scared? No. But it's a stupid test.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你疯了吗？也许吧，你怕了吗？没有，但这测试很白痴。

yingyinNormal.en: Just take the test. You need to know if you and Chuck are gonna have a baby.
yingyinNormal.zh: 测试一下，你要确定一下，你是不是怀了恰克的孩子。

yingyinNormal.en: This place, it's not what we thought it was. It's not a prison, it's a test.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这地方，并不是我们想的那样，这不是牢笼，是个测试。

yingyinNormal.en: I had to ask you something. You weren't sick the day you took your aptitude test, were you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要问你一些事，你派别倾向测试那天并没有生病，对吧？

yingyinNormal.en: You paid that? Free trial. I took the test to see if I qualify for the free trial.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你付款了吗？免费试听，我做了测试，看看我符不符合免费试听资格。

yingyinNormal.en: We have only three passing scores on the deep space navigation test. Alai, Bean and Ender.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只有三个学员通过了深空导航测试，有阿莱和小豆子，还有安德。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's just take the test. No, no, no, I don't want to. Oh, well, 'cause you know we're gonna do bad.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们接受测试。不，我不想。因为你知道我们的分数会很差。

yingyinNormal.en: Surrender your gun and badge. And your next baseline test is out of my hands. Thank you, madam.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把你的枪和警徽交出来。你下次基准测试我就管不着了。谢谢长官。

yingyinNormal.en: Our hosts began to pass the Turing test after the first year. But that wasn't enough for Arnold.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一年后，接待员们开始通过了图灵测试，但是阿诺德不满足于此。

yingyinNormal.en: The answer is one simple test away. You know, it's like when I thought there was a possum in my closet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一个简单测试便知答案，就像那次我以为我的衣柜里有负鼠一样。

examination_example.sentence: Surveys and <highlight>test</highlight> samples have also become important for understanding the larger landscapes that contain archaeological sites.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 调查和测试样本对于了解包含考古遗址的更大景观也变得很重要。

examination_example.sentence: They often include a certain amount of digging to <highlight>test</highlight> for buried materials at selected points across a landscape.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它们通常包括一定量的挖掘，以测试景观中选定点的掩埋材料。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了验证这个想法，他转向了大学招生程序。

examination_example.sentence: The bar exam is truly a stern enough <highlight>test</highlight> for a would-be lawyer.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 律师考试对一个想成为律师的人来说确实是一个足够严峻的考验。

examination_example.sentence: Some students might do well on state <highlight>tests</highlight> without completing their homework.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有些学生可能在没有完成作业的情况下，在州考中表现不错。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 法院应该限制基因测试。

examination_example.sentence: Genetic <highlight>tests</highlight> are not reliable
examination_example.sentence_trans: 基因测试不可靠。

examination_example.sentence: Last year a federal task-force urged reform for patents related to genetic <highlight>tests</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 去年，一个联邦特别工作组敦促改革与基因测试相关的专利。

examination_example.sentence: Australia's MAAL (multinational anti-avoidance law), and India's SEP (significant economic presence) <highlight>test</highlight>, to name but a few.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 仅举几个例子，澳大利亚的多国反避税法和印度的重要经济存在测试。

examination_example.sentence: Legal scholars say the Vermont case will offer a precedent-setting <highlight>test</highlight> of how far those powers extend.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但法律学者表示，佛蒙特州案将为这些权力的延伸提供一个创先例的测试。

examination_example.sentence: In the author's view, the Vermont case will <highlight>test</highlight> the limits of states’ power over nuclear issues.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在作者看来，佛蒙特案将考验各州在核问题上的权力极限。

examination_example.sentence: King Solomon will <highlight>test</highlight> whether Amram's story is true．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 所罗门王将检验暗兰的故事是否真实。

examination_example.sentence: To <highlight>test</highlight> this, some researchers did an experiment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了验证这一点，一些研究人员做了一个实验。

word_usage.usage: test可以是名词，可以是动词，作为名词时前面要加冠词the或a，如put to the test(试验)。
